    "form_header_text": "Appropriations Programmatic and Language Requests",
    "form_instructions_text": "Please use this form to submit programmatic and language requests to Rep. Conaway's office for the FY27 Appropriations process. The office will only consider requests with a direct connection to NJ-03 and New Jersey. Programmatic/Bill and Report Language requests are general funding requests for national and regional programs, and/or bill and report language requests that direct, encourage, or urge an Agency or Department to carry out an action (e.g. robust funding for the NIH, \"the Committee directs the NIH to advance rare disease research\"). They are NOT requests for specific projects/specific entities. Do not use this form to submit requests for Community Project Funding/Congressionally Directed Spending. Please fill out one form per request. If you or your organization submit more than one request, please rank the importance of each request in the final question of this form. Our deadline for submissions is March 6, 2026. This deadline is subject to change based on the House Appropriations Committee submission deadlines. Our Office cannot guarantee that the Congressman will support every request submitted. If you have any questions, please contact Rep. Conaway's Deputy Chief of Staff, Laney O'Shea at Appropriations.herbconaway@mail.house.gov.",
